2019-11-21.text: Oh lordy it's Christmas for me, got two Crystal Exarch keychains, and my special edition Fruits Basket set in the mail today.

2019-11-15.text:
Got to play some Pokemon Sword last night and I've never seen my fiance get so salty over me seeing a Haunter first and getting a good chunk of levels off said pokemon. (I wasn't able to catch it cause it was too high of a level.)
So far I'm enjoying the game. ^^

2019-11-04.text: Wish you the best of luck, if you find yourself stuck on a certain part you're more than welcome to message me and I'll help the best I can. ^^

What I've learned to do with meteors is face them north and south, your tanks will be out of the way so they won't get clipped and meteors go off right after the second set of meteors. Hopefully that's helpful. ^^

2019-11-01.text: It's been one of those weeks where I just want to sleep for days because I'm physically and mentally exhausted. 😖
